| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4736 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c1e4fc9b-ddc1-5b5e-a687-b34adfcb85cf"
